{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "examia-backend-collection",
		"name": "Examia Backend API",
		"description": "Colección de endpoints para la API de Examia Backend.\n\n## Entornos disponibles:\n- **Local**: http://localhost:8080\n- **Producción**: https://examia-backend-tzwg.onrender.com\n\n## Flujo de autenticación:\n1. Login (POST /api/auth/login) - Guarda el token automáticamente\n2. Usar endpoints protegidos con el token\n\n**Nota**: Los usuarios son cargados directamente en la base de datos por un administrador.\n\n## Variables:\n- `baseUrl`: URL base del servidor\n- `token`: Token JWT (se guarda automáticamente después del login)",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "baseUrl",
			"value": "http://localhost:8080",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "token",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Auth",
			"description": "Endpoints de autenticación (públicos)",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Health Check",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/health",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "health"]
						},
						"description": "Verifica que el servicio de autenticación esté funcionando."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Actuator Health",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/actuator/health",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["actuator", "health"]
						},
						"description": "Health check de Spring Boot Actuator. Usado por Render para verificar que la app está viva."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', jsonData.token);",
									"    console.log('Token guardado automáticamente');",
									"    console.log('Usuario:', jsonData.email, '- Rol:', jsonData.role);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"test@examia.com\",\n    \"password\": \"test123456\"\n}",
							"options": {
								"raw": {
									"language": "json"
								}
							}
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
						},
						"description": "Inicia sesión con un usuario existente.\n\n**El token se guarda automáticamente** en la variable `{{token}}` para usarlo en requests protegidos.\n\n**Respuestas:**\n- `200 OK`: Login exitoso, devuelve token JWT\n- `404 Not Found`: Usuario no existe\n- `401 Unauthorized`: Contraseña incorrecta"
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "Login exitoso",
							"originalRequest": {
								"method": "POST",
								"header": [
									{
										"key": "Content-Type",
										"value": "application/json"
									}
								],
								"body": {
									"mode": "raw",
									"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"test@examia.com\",\n    \"password\": \"test123456\"\n}"
								},
								"url": {
									"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
									"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
									"path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
								}
							},
							"status": "OK",
							"code": 200,
							"_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
							"header": [
								{
									"key": "Content-Type",
									"value": "application/json"
								}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n    \"email\": \"test@examia.com\",\n    \"nombre\": \"Test\",\n    \"apellido\": \"Usuario\",\n    \"role\": \"PROFESOR\",\n    \"message\": \"Inicio de sesión exitoso\"\n}"
						},
						{
							"name": "Usuario no encontrado",
							"originalRequest": {
								"method": "POST",
								"header": [
									{
										"key": "Content-Type",
										"value": "application/json"
									}
								],
								"body": {
									"mode": "raw",
									"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"noexiste@ejemplo.com\",\n    \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
								},
								"url": {
									"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
									"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
									"path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
								}
							},
							"status": "Not Found",
							"code": 404,
							"_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
							"header": [
								{
									"key": "Content-Type",
									"value": "application/json"
								}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"status\": 404,\n    \"error\": \"Not Found\",\n    \"message\": \"No existe un usuario con el email 'noexiste@ejemplo.com'\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-14T15:30:00\",\n    \"path\": \"/api/auth/login\"\n}"
						},
						{
							"name": "Contraseña incorrecta",
							"originalRequest": {
								"method": "POST",
								"header": [
									{
										"key": "Content-Type",
										"value": "application/json"
									}
								],
								"body": {
									"mode": "raw",
									"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"test@examia.com\",\n    \"password\": \"passwordIncorrecta\"\n}"
								},
								"url": {
									"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
									"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
									"path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
								}
							},
							"status": "Unauthorized",
							"code": 401,
							"_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
							"header": [
								{
									"key": "Content-Type",
									"value": "application/json"
								}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"status\": 401,\n    \"error\": \"Unauthorized\",\n    \"message\": \"La contraseña es incorrecta para el usuario 'test@examia.com'\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-14T15:30:00\",\n    \"path\": \"/api/auth/login\"\n}"
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Endpoints Protegidos (Ejemplo)",
			"description": "Ejemplos de cómo usar endpoints que requieren autenticación.\n\nEstos endpoints aún no están implementados, pero muestran cómo configurar el header Authorization.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "[Ejemplo] Endpoint Protegido",
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "bearer",
							"bearer": [
								{
									"key": "token",
									"value": "{{token}}",
									"type": "string"
								}
							]
						},
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/ejemplo/protegido",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["api", "ejemplo", "protegido"]
						},
						"description": "**EJEMPLO** - Este endpoint no existe todavía.\n\nMuestra cómo configurar el header Authorization con el token JWT.\n\nEl token se toma automáticamente de la variable `{{token}}` que se guarda después del login."
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		}
	]
}

